Durajadi Simba murume ari mu[[hushangazhi]] hwema[[bhanga]] umo vanoshanda neRoyal Bank. VaSimba mumwe wavana [[sakuwana]] vakavamba Bhanga iri. Pari zvino vanoshanda vari [[mukokeri]] muRoyal Bank.

VaDurajadi Simba vashanda makore anosvika makumi matatu nematatu (33) muhushangazhi hwemaBhanga. Vakatanga vachishandira Standard Chartered Bank mugore ra1975. Nokufamba kwenguva vakapinda muzvigaro zvikuru zvohutunganiriri nemakambani anoti: Syfrets; First Merchant Bank neFirst Banking Group.

VaSimba vnaobata zvakare vari [[Mufundisi]] muKereke yeGlad Tidings mu[[Harare]].

Murume uyu ndiye zvakare sakuwana we[[Zambuko Trust]] rinova sangano rinopa zvikwereti kumabhizinisi madiki muZimbabwe.

VaDurajadi Simba mumwe werudzi rwava[[Remba]]
